Package: trace
Title: Tandem Repeat Analysis by Capillary Electrophoresis
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Zachariah", "McLean", , "zachariah.louis.mclean@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-0968-0538"))
Description: The goal of package is to provide a pipeline for short tandem repeat instability analysis from fragment analysis data. This package takes inputs of fsa files or peak tables (eg Genemapper5 software output), and a user supplied metadata data-frame. The package identifies ladders, calls peaks, identifies the modal peaks, calls repeats, then calculates repeat instability metrics (ie expansion index or average repeat gain).
